This is a simple React app that shows a countdown timer for New Year's Eve (January 1, 2025). Once the countdown reaches zero, it displays a "Happy New Year!" message along with the current time. The app is fully responsive and works well on both mobile and desktop devices.

Features:
- Real-time countdown to New Year.
- Displays the current time.
- Fully responsive design for all screen sizes.

Technologies Used:
- React
- Tailwind CSS
- JavaScript (ES6)

https://github.com/Turdugul/new-year-coundown
